</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Den edeln und vesten, des hochgeporn fürsten, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>rczog</expan> Ludweigs
                        von Bayern, reten. </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als her Wyrich von
                                <expan>Treuhtling<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        schultheisz, <add>vormals mit ew</add> geredt hat von der
                                <expan>lantschranne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czu Hirssperg, darümb senden wir
                                    <add><expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan></add> czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Hofner, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, mit ew <add>auch</add> davon czu reden. Und
                                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc. ut in
                            <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
